data.description: A rare find with this 5 bedroom home! Come take a look and think of what you can do with all this space! Mature trees and Huge back yard!   For the person who likes to work out their garage with either woodworking or other crafts even working on motorcycles, you will love the extra deep garage that has a seperate work area! Lots of natural light and looks like the previous owner had a furnace in this exta work area too!   Main floor is open floor plan. Large laundry room on main level as well.
